Name: Windows Template Library (WTL)
Short Name: wtl
URL: https://www.nuget.org/packages/wtl/
Version: 10.1.0
License: MS-PL
License File: Ms-PL.txt
Security Critical: yes
Shipped: yes
Update Mechanism: Manual
CPEPrefix: cpe:/a:microsoft:windows_template_library
Description:
WTL is a C++ library for developing Windows applications and UI components.
It extends ATL (Active Template Library) and provides a set of classes for
controls, dialogues, frame windows, and GDI objects.

Local Modifications:
- Substitutions in install.sh to fix calls to `ATLVERIFY` to avoid unused
  variable warnings in release builds.
